.TH "get_line_length" 9 "get_line_length" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
get_line_length \- calculates buffer pitch in bytes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u32" get_line_length
.BI "(struct i810fb_par *par "  ","
.BI "int xres_virtual "  ","
.BI "int bpp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "par" 12
pointer to i810fb_par structure
.IP "xres_virtual" 12
virtual resolution of the frame
.IP "bpp" 12
bits per pixel
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Calculates buffer pitch in bytes.  
